Subject: Re: [VB] Paint order... top, then bottom? bottom, then top?

 Hi Conrad,
Yes, somewhere after about the change over to 1962 model year the buses were
then painted the top color inside and out.  Then the lower color was painted
only on exterior.

  Before 1962 the bus was painted inside and out with lower color and then the
top was painted the upper color.
